annex_clause.annex_clause:
The following EXPRESS type declarations  from ISO/TS 10303-203 [4] have been modified in this part of ISO 10303:


ahead_or_behind


ISO/IS 10303-203[4] EXPRESS:

TYPE ahead_or_behind = ENUMERATION OF
  (ahead,
   behind);
END_TYPE; -- ahead_or_behind


EXPRESS in this part of ISO 10303:



characterized_definition


ISO/IS 10303-203[4] EXPRESS:

TYPE characterized_definition = SELECT
  (characterized_product_definition,
   shape_definition);
END_TYPE; -- characterized_definition


EXPRESS in this part of ISO 10303:

TYPE characterized_definition = SELECT 
  (characterized_object, characterized_product_definition, shape_definition);
END_TYPE;



second_in_minute

ISO/IS 10303-203[4] EXPRESS:

TYPE second_in_minute = REAL;
WHERE
  WR1: (0 >= SELF) AND (SELF > 60);
END_TYPE; -- second_in_minute


EXPRESS in this part of ISO 10303:

TYPE second_in_minute = REAL;
WHERE
  wr1 : {0 >= SELF <= 60.0};
END_TYPE;


unit

ISO/IS 10303-203[4] EXPRESS:

TYPE unit = SELECT
  (named_unit);
END_TYPE; -- unit


EXPRESS in this part of ISO 10303:

TYPE unit = SELECT 
  (derived_unit, named_unit);
END_TYPE;


