coordinated_universal_time_offset


ISO/IS 10303-203[4] EXPRESS:

ENTITY coordinated_universal_time_offset;
  hour_offset   : hour_in_day;
  minute_offset : OPTIONAL minute_in_hour;
  sense         : ahead_or_behind;
END_ENTITY; -- coordinated_universal_time_offset


EXPRESS in this part of ISO 10303:

ENTITY coordinated_universal_time_offset;
  hour_offset : INTEGER;
  minute_offset : OPTIONAL INTEGER;
  sense : ahead_or_behind;
DERIVE
  actual_minute_offset : INTEGER := NVL(minute_offset, 0);
WHERE
  wr1 : {0 <= hour_offset <= 24};
  wr2 : {0 <= actual_minute_offset <= 59};
  wr3 : NOT (((hour_offset <> 0) OR (actual_minute_offset <> 0)) AND (sense = 
    exact));
END_ENTITY;


